The defendant JAMIE L. RUSSELL was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case.

  • Possession of Methamphetamine, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(g).
  • Disorderly Conduct, a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
